# AGENTS.md — {{name}}

## Overview

This is a RunAgents agent that handles user requests using the platform's tool mesh and LLM gateway.

## Tools

Configured in `runagents.yaml`. Each tool is an external API registered on the platform.
The agent calls tools via `agent.call_tool(name, path, payload)` — the mesh handles auth tokens.

## Development

```bash
runagents dev    # Local dev server with mock tools
```

## Deployment

```bash
runagents deploy # Ship to the platform
```
